{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"toefl-sentences","unitId":"sentence-018","title":"Sentence 18","sectionId":"sentences-011","sectionTitle":"Sentence 11-20","pageStart":130,"pageEnd":135,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":49,"duplicateEntryCount":2,"pages":[{"number":130,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Sentence 18"},{"type":"text","text":"The worker and soldier castes of termites consist of both males and"},{"type":"text","text":"females, and the queen lives permanently with a male consort."},{"type":"text","text":"白蚁中的工蚁和兵蚁的阶层由雄性和雌性共同组成，而女王永"},{"type":"text","text":"久地和一个雄性配偶生活在一起。"},{"type":"section","text":"语法笔记"},{"type":"text","text":"本句由and连接两个并列句构成。第一个分句的主干是the castes"},{"type":"text","text":"consist of both males and females；第二个分句的主干是the queen lives"},{"type":"text","text":"with a consort。"},{"type":"section","text":"核心词表"},{"type":"entry","text":"caste /kæst/ n. 社会阶层；社会等级","headword":"caste"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 the ruling caste 统治阶级"},{"type":"entry","text":"termite /ˈtɜːrmaɪt/ n. 白蚁","headword":"termite"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 a termite colony 白蚁群"},{"type":"entry","text":"male /meɪl/ n. 雄性动（植）物；男性","headword":"male"},{"type":"definition","text":"a. 雄性的"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 male ant 雄蚁"},{"type":"entry","text":"female /ˈfiːmeɪl/ n. 雌性动（植）物；女性","headword":"female"},{"type":"definition","text":"a. 雌性的；女性的"},{"type":"note","text":"参考 feminine a. 女性的；妇女的"}]},{"number":131,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"permanently /ˈpɜːrmənəntli/ ad. 永久地","headword":"permanently"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 permanent a. 永久的"},{"type":"text","text":"permanency n. 永存"},{"type":"entry","text":"consort /ˈkɑːnsɔːrt/ n. （尤指统治者的）配偶","headword":"consort"},{"type":"definition","text":"vi. 结交，配对"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 the prince consort 亲王（女王的丈夫）"},{"type":"section","text":"主题归纳"},{"type":"text","text":"与“节肢动物”相关的词："},{"type":"entry","text":"arthropod /ˈɑːrθrəpɑːd/ n. 节肢动物","headword":"arthropod"},{"type":"entry","text":"insect /ˈɪnsekt/ n. 昆虫","headw